n```\\n\\n</details>\\n\",\"structuredPatch\":[{\"oldStart\":540,\"oldLines\":6,\"newStart\":540,\"newLines\":21,\"lines\":[\" **Position:** Message count (`len(transcript.Messages)`).\",\" **Offset:** Start iterating messages at index N.\",\" \",\"+### JSON Format (OpenCode pattern)\",\"+\",\"+Single JSON object with `info` and `messages` array. Messages contain `parts` (text, tool calls with state). Similar to Gemini's pattern but with a different schema:\",\"+\",\"+```json\",\"+{\\\"info\\\": {\\\"id\\\": \\\"...\\\", \\\"title\\\": \\\"...\\\"}, \\\"messages\\\": [{\\\"info\\\": {\\\"role\\\": \\\"user\\\"}, \\\"parts\\\": [{\\\"type\\\": \\\"text\\\", \\\"text\\\": \\\"...\\\"}]}]}\",\"+```\",\"+\",\"+Key difference: OpenCode stores transcripts in a database, not files. The transcript is fetched via `opencode export <sessionID>` at turn-end and cached to `.entire/tmp/<sessionID>.json`.\",\"+\",\"+**Chunking:** Parse JSON, distribute messages across chunks (each chunk is complete JSON with `info` + subset of `messages`).\",\"+**Reassembly:** Merge message arrays from all chunks, preserve `info` from first chunk.\",\"+**Position:** Message count (`len(session.Messages)`).\",\"+**Offset:** Start iterating messages at index N.\",\"+\",\" ### Using Chunking Helpers\",\" \",\" The `agent` package provides format-agnostic entry points:\"]}],\"userModified\":false,\"replaceAll\":false},\"sourceToolAssistantUUID\":\"1edc96a4-1bb8-46ee-b54c-99fce2ad2f74\"}\n{\"parentUuid\":\"f0308a30-0e0b-46cb-aec8-0b3b529f18d5\",\"isSidechain\":false,\"userType\":\"external\",\"cwd\":\"/Users/gtrrz-victor/wks/cli/old-prs\",\"sessionId\":\"cc955527-f968-4362-ae8c-6ffab1276178\",\"version\":\"2.1.52\",\"gitBranch\":\"gtrrz-victor/add-opencode-docs\",\"slug\":\"refactored-finding-creek\",\"message\":{\"model\":\"claude-opus-4-6\",\"id\":\"msg_019Lkc1yUUUbiJGveQ2Mjntj\",\"type\":\"message\",\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"id\":\"toolu_01CLsx5PLSkzd36dEtBBUepV\",